These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 6

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-1::.
4 different pets are kept: mouse, chinchilla, turtle, rabbit
There are 4 different favourite colors: mauve, amber, emerald, chestnut
1. the person who likes mauve is somewhere to the left of the person who likes emerald##5
2. the owner of the chinchilla is not the person who likes mauve##6
3. the person who likes mauve is on the right of the person who likes chestnut##1
4. the owner of the turtle is on the right of the person who likes emerald##1
5. the owner of the mouse is on the right of the person who likes mauve##1
6. the person who likes mauve is not the owner of the turtle##6

.:: Answer ::.
|            |     1      |    2     |    3     |    4    |
| Beverage   | chinchilla   | rabbit    | mouse    | turtle |
| Sport      | chestnut | mauve | emerald | amber |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-2::.
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: august, november, january, march
The people use 4 different means of transport: subway, helicopter, train, jet-ski
1. the person driving the subway is on the far right##1
2. the person who's birthday is in november is somewhere to the left of the person who's birthday is in january##5
3. the person driving the jet-ski is somewhere to the left of the person who's birthday is in march##5
4. the person who's birthday is in november is not the person driving the helicopter##6
5. the person driving the jet-ski is on the left of the person who's birthday is in january##1
6. the person driving the subway is on the right of the person driving the train##1
7. the person who's birthday is in march is on the right of the person who's birthday is in august##1
8. the person who's birthday is in january is somewhere to the left of the person who's birthday is in august##5

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1   |     2      |    3     |     4     |
| Beverage   | november  | january    | august | march    |
| Food       | jet-ski | helicopter | train  | subway |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-3::.
City: rome, hannover, liverpool, berlin
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: november, january, december, may
1. the person traveling to berlin is not the person who's birthday is in november##6
2. the person who's birthday is in january is not the person traveling to liverpool##6
3. the person who's birthday is in december is on the left or right of the person traveling to hannover##3
4. the person who's birthday is in january is the person traveling to rome##1
5. the person traveling to hannover is on the left of the person who's birthday is in january##1
6. the person traveling to rome is in an odd position##4
7. the person who's birthday is in november is on the far left or far right##3
8. the person who's birthday is in december is somewhere to the left of the person who's birthday is in may##5

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1      |       2        |   3    |   4    |
| Beverage   | berlin       | hannover  | rome  | liverpool |
| Job        | december | may | january | november  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-4::.
4 different games are played: whist, billiard, poker, monopoly
The people have 4 different hobbies: chess, rock-climbing, cooking, filmmaking
1. the person playing poker is on the left of the person playing monopoly##1
2. the person playing billiard is somewhere to the left of the person who's hobby is chess##5
3. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is not the person playing billiard##6
4. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is chess##5
5. the person who's hobby is cooking is on the right of the person who's hobby is rock-climbing##1
6. the person playing monopoly is somewhere to the left of the person who's hobby is filmmaking##5

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |    2     |     3     |    4     |
| Pet         | billiard | poker | monopoly     | whist |
| Transport   | rock-climbing     | cooking    | chess | filmmaking    |

