.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-5::.
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: golf, weightlifting, basketball, cricket
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: r&b, d&b, dubstep, house
1. the person who's sport is golf is on the left of the person who's sport is cricket##1
2. the person who's sport is cricket is somewhere to the left of the fan dubstep##5
3. the person who's sport is cricket is somewhere to the left of the fan d&b##5
4. the person who's sport is weightlifting is not the fan house##6
5. the fan r&b is not the person who's sport is golf##6
6. the person who's sport is basketball is on the left of the person who's sport is weightlifting##1
7. the fan dubstep is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |  2   |    3     |   4   |
| Beverage    | golf        | cricket | basketball | weightlifting |
| Transport   | house | r&b | d&b     | dubstep   |

