.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-6::.
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: amaryllis, rose, marigold, sunflower
The people have 4 different jobs:  dancer, writer, photographer, chef
1. the dancer is on the right of the person who growsamaryllis##1
2. the person who growssunflower is not the writer##6
3. the dancer is on the far right##1
4. the writer is somewhere to the right of the chef##5
5. the person who growsmarigold is the person who growsmarigold##1
6. the person who growsmarigold is somewhere to the left of the dancer##5
7. the person who growsmarigold is somewhere to the left of the person who growsamaryllis##5
8. the person who growsrose is somewhere to the left of the chef##5
9. the person who growsrose is somewhere to the left of the chef##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |   2    |     3     |     4      |
| Movie-Genre   | rose | marigold    | amaryllis  | sunflower   |
| Nationality   | photographer  | chef | writer | dancer |

