.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-7::.
There 4 different types of food: artichoke, pomegranate, cabbage, radish
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: badminton, ice-hockey, golf, skiing
1. the person who's sport is golf is on the left or right of the person who's sport is badminton##3
2. the person who's sport is golf is not the person eating pomegranate##6
3. the person eating artichoke is the person who's sport is ice-hockey##1
4. the person who's sport is badminton is on the left or right of the person who's sport is skiing##3
5. the person who's sport is golf is on the far left##1
6. the person eating pomegranate is the person who's sport is badminton##1
7. the person eating radish is somewhere to the left of the person who's sport is badminton##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2    |      3      |      4      |
| Movie-Genre   | radish | pomegranate     | cabbage | artichoke |
| Music-Genre   | golf | badminton | skiing      | ice-hockey         |

