.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-8::.
4 different pets are kept: cat, hamster, mouse, rat
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: country, gospel, metal, soul
1. the fan country is on the left of the fan gospel##1
2. the fan soul is somewhere to the left of the fan metal##5
3. the fan soul is on the right of the fan gospel##1
4. the fan gospel is on the left or right of the owner of the hamster##3
5. the owner of the mouse is on the left or right of the fan gospel##3
6. the fan country is on the left or right of the owner of the cat##3
7. the owner of the rat is somewhere to the right of the owner of the mouse##5
8. the owner of the hamster is not the fan soul##6

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1   |     2      |       3       |      4       |
| Beverage   | hamster  | cat        | mouse      | rat          |
| Job        | country | gospel | soul | metal |

