.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-10::.
The people use 4 different means of transport: scooter, jet-ski, trike, taxi
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: documentary, western, family, fantasy
1. the person watching documentary movies is not the person driving the scooter##6
2. the person driving the taxi is on the left of the person driving the jet-ski##1
3. the person watching fantasy movies is the person watching fantasy movies##1
4. the person driving the taxi is on the right of the person watching fantasy movies##1
5. the person driving the trike is not the person watching fantasy movies##6
6. the person watching western movies is not the person driving the jet-ski##6
7. the person watching fantasy movies is in an even position##4
8. the person driving the trike is the person watching documentary movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1     |       2       |    3    |    4     |
| Pet     | trike | scooter        | taxi  | jet-ski     |
| Sport   | documentary     | fantasy | western | family |

