.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-11::.
4 different pets are kept: turtle, lizard, rabbit, frog
There are 4 different nationalities: nigerian, argentine, dutch, polish
1. the owner of the turtle is on the left or right of the owner of the frog##3
2. the argentine is somewhere to the left of the owner of the turtle##5
3. the dutch is not the owner of the rabbit##6
4. the owner of the lizard is between the polish and the owner of the rabbit##2
5. the owner of the rabbit is on the left of the owner of the lizard##1
6. the argentine is between the nigerian and the owner of the turtle##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |     2      |   3   |     4     |
| Hobby         | rabbit | lizard    | turtle | frog |
| Music-Genre   | nigerian         | argentine | polish   | dutch     |

