.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-12::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  musician, manager, social-worker, lawyer
City: venice, marseilles, paris, rome
1. the social-worker is somewhere to the right of the person traveling to paris##5
2. the lawyer is not the person traveling to venice##6
3. the person traveling to marseilles is the lawyer##1
4. the person traveling to marseilles is on the right of the manager##1
5. the person traveling to paris is not the lawyer##6
6. the manager is not the person traveling to venice##6
7. the social-worker is somewhere to the left of the manager##5
8. the musician is on the left of the social-worker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |    2     |     3     |   4    |
| Food        | musician  | social-worker | manager | lawyer |
| Transport   | paris | venice     | rome     | marseilles    |

