There are 4 different nationalities: mexican, canadian, german, chinese
1. the person who's sport is basketball is somewhere to the right of the person who's sport is snowboarding##5
2. the person who's sport is snowboarding is not the canadian##6
3. the person who's sport is basketball is the chinese##1
4. the person who's sport is water-polo is somewhere to the right of the canadian##5
5. the person who's sport is basketball is between the person who's sport is snowboarding and the mexican##2
6. the person who's sport is snowboarding is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |      2      |     3     |     4     |
| Food          | cycling | snowboarding      | basketball | water-polo   |
| Movie-Genre   | canadian     | german | chinese   | mexican |

