3. the person who's birthday is in december is not the person traveling to london##6
4. the person who's birthday is in october is on the left of the person who's birthday is in december##1
5. the person who's birthday is in april is between the person traveling to hannover and the person who's birthday is in december##2
6. the person traveling to hannover is not the person who's birthday is in october##6
7. the person traveling to liverpool is on the right of the person traveling to paris##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1     |    2     |     3     |     4      |
| Job     | london  | paris | liverpool | hannover |
| Sport   | october | december | april   | february |

