1. the prince-smoker is somewhere to the right of the tiparillo-smoker##5
2. the siglo-smoker is somewhere to the right of the prince-smoker##5
3. the prince-smoker is on the left of the siglo-smoker##1
4. the dannemann-smoker is not the person playing domino##6
5. the person playing bridge is between the person playing domino and the person playing monopoly##2
6. the person playing billiard is on the far left or far right##3
7. the person playing billiard is on the right of the person playing domino##1
8. the dannemann-smoker is somewhere to the right of the prince-smoker##5

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |     2     |      3      |      4      |
| Hobby   | monopoly | bridge | domino | billiard |
| Pet     | tiparillo  | prince      | siglo  | dannemann       |

