2. the photographer is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is photography##3
3. the person who's hobby is sudoku is on the right of the person who's hobby is filmmaking##1
4. the person who's hobby is sudoku is not the entrepreneur##6
5. the photographer is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is photography##5
6. the person who's hobby is photography is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|             |      1      |    2     |     3      |     4     |
| Beverage    | entrepreneur | coach | photographer      | analyst   |
| Transport   | drawing  | photography   | filmmaking | sudoku |

 